{"tid":1220992,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"［建築學生撚］求建築laptop 2019 有咩好介紹？","createTime":"2019-06-14T06:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T08:58:27.000Z","uid":251257,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"f877efe33cd86e9e81d7c628deda34037119174e","tid":1220992,"uid":251257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-14T06:14:38.000Z","msg":"之前部電腦已經用左好耐，壽終正寢<br />\n<br />\n黎緊去year 3，想問有冇邊款好推介？<br />\n主要用既有Sketchup, Vray, PS, AI, <br />\n因為自己都有興趣攝影拍攝, 所以LR, Pr Pro 都會用到<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n筆直大概 12-15K, 學生哥冇咩錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n上網做左啲research<br />\n<br />\n依家睇到<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">1.)2018 Dell XPS 9570 Laptop</span><br />\nCore  i7-8750H 4.1 GHz<br />\n  32GB RAM DDR4<br />\n  NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050Ti 4GB vRAM<br />\n  1TB SSD PCIe NVMe<br />\n  15.6&rdquo; UHD Touch IPS <br />\n  3.97lbs<br />\n  8 hours</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">2.)Apple 15&quot; MacBook Pro</span><br />\nRetina, Touch Bar, 2.9GHz Intel Core i7 Quad Core, 16GB RAM, 512GB SSD,</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">3.)Microsoft Surface Book 2 </span><br />\nIntel Core i7, 16GB RAM, 1TB NVIDIA GTX 1050 2GB GDDR5 vRAM) - 13.5 &ldquo; </strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">4.) Dell Prevision</span></strong><br />\n<strong>Core i7-6280 up to 4.1GHz<br />\n  16GB RAM DDR4<br />\n   NVIDIA Quadro M1000 2GB vRAM<br />\n  256GB SSD PCIe NVMe<br />\n  15.6&rdquo; full HD IPS<br />\n  4lb<br />\n  11 hours</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">5.)MSI GL62M</span></strong><br />\n<strong>Core  i7-7700HQ 3.8GHz8GB RAM DDR4<br />\n  NVIDIA GeForce GTX 1050TI 4GB vRAM<br />\n  1TB 5400RPM + 128GB SSD<br />\n  15&rdquo; Full HD 1080p<br />\n  5.66 lb<br />\n  4-6 hours</strong><br />\n<br />\n有啲真係太重，成舊石頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n請問呢幾款有冇邊部比較好？<br />\n或者有冇其他提議<